</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_268" id="133v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Friczen Hofman, <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> czu Frankford </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Fridrich, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                    <add><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> Possen und</add>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Trosp<ex>er</ex>gs</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers,
                        wegen, des danken wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntschaft mit
                                <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz <add>und
                                    <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> das gern umb ew verschulden</add>
                        und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darümb den
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> czu rede gesaczt und in
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief hören lassen und der wirdt ew selber
                        ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darümb
                        <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.</ab>
</div>
